              h5.center API
              p.light
                | While a majority of these raw datasets are available through opencolorado.org and CKAN, the need for a concise JSON API serving data relevant to Denver still exists. DenverCharts API aims to fill this gap with a platform allowing community developers to combine and  share civic data sets in new ways.
          .col.s12.m4
            .icon-block
              h2.center.brown-text
